name: deep_codegen_cross_unless_set_conj_then_contains
section: codegen-cross-feature
args: p:Bool a:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: unless must guard set mutation and contains? must reflect the mutation.
law: (= (with [s (set)] (do (unless {p} (conj! s {a})) (contains? s {a}))) (not {p}))
